Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.99,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I explained just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it would be extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.21,0:00:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if all went well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand... At least I think I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've talked about it with\Nboth my mother and father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up for this. I want to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:04.03,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Music Preperation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:09.37,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori Miyazono\N[Connected]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, you're off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, that's normal in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't feel threatened! You're slacking off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've got the étude, too, you know!\NYou have your back against the wall!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you get that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I get it! Don't talk about\Nit, you'll make me panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were short on prep\Ntime from the start,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but thanks to all that flirting\Nwith that junior high girl...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't flirting with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.34,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of convo is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were too flirting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:27.76,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're fighting over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Were too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:28.13,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[Connected]\NArima
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:28.39,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Call Ended
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-chan! Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Just look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, I only got a C.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll try for another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsubaki. How'd you\Ndo on your mock exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:51.45,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance Exam Results - By School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scored a B. Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, that bumbling gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, Miss Muscles-for-brains?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only asked her because I was\Nsure she scored lower than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she's Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I rule. Bow down before me, you dullards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:22.11,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.57,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who said I\Nhad to check in regularly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She took a turn for the worse...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? Should I wait for her?\NIf I ask the nurse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what do you know? Arima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miyazono-san's mother and father...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to visit Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's... nothing. But I\Ncan't find her anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I know where she must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going, slowly now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put your left foot out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She says she doesn't want to lose her stamina or muscle strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rehabilitation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She says that she wants to play\Nthe violin onstage, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.88,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rehabilitation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break, Kaori-chan.\NYou're trying to do too much at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal. Violinists have\Nmore stamina than you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to you, Arima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori had given up... she'd thrown in the towel,\Nreally... And now she's starting to walk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One sure step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you did was show\Ndevotion, right, Arima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that devotion was what\Nstruck a chord in Kaori's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it gives me only a little more time,\Neven if there's only the slightest hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to cling to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was a boy that I met in April.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cried and vomited, and struggled\Nso hard it was unseemly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But onstage, I shone like a star, and my life\Nseemed like a gorgeous rendition of a melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise with that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "Let's perform together again."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to struggle as hard as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how unseemly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...or futile it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,struggle like there's no tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm one of them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I go on wallowing in\Nmy despair, and just give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can never face my parents, who\Ngave birth to me, and raised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I just give up now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel sorry for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That devotion you showed, Arima-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori's heart had turned gray, and you gave it color.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:48.90,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Library        New Arrivals
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's been playing the piano all through\Nthe night. Every night, these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know the competition's coming up soon,\Nbut it's right after the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will he do okay on his entrance\Nexams? That Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's Arima-kun's\Nway of studying to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. To get into a\Nmusic-oriented high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sure they test you on regular subjects\Ntoo, but achievements trump all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those schools want to burnish their reputations\Nby admitting the top performers at competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since Arima-kun hasn't\Ncompeted in the last two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he's sorely lacking in\Nterms of achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now the Eastern Japan Piano\NCompetition is coming up in December.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's got a long history,\Nand cachet like no other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So for the school, there's\Nno better advertisement
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,than admitting the cream of the\Ncrop from that competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, to get to the top of the heap\Nat the Eastern Japan Piano Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is the same for Arima-kun as\Npassing an entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like hitting a walk-off homerun, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you stop being\Njealous of music, and root for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am not jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than having him\Nflunk and head overseas, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now might be my\Nonly chance to be near him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima-kun must be exhausted,\Nplaying so late into the night, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you brought some food\Nover, I'm sure he'd be thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm doing this\Nbecause Kashiwagi told me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei, you're so light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A Tosa dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Tsubaki. Was I asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sleep like you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been playing non-stop? You're\Npushing yourself a little too hard, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The required Bach piece... The Bach piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your room's a total mess!\NWould it kill you tidy up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so bothersome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you showing up at the\Ncompetition with that hairdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you can do this?\NYou need a license, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always just cut my own\Nhair when I need a little trim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By cutting your own hair, you\Njust mean your bangs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go the barbershop, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're only going to think it's\Na pain in the butt and not go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the whining!\NAccept your fate if you're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-P-P-Please, I'm counting on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cutting too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, no sweat! Remember how\NI used to do this for you when we were kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The competition's coming up soon, so I'm\Ngonna make you look like a stud, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like I'm usually a real tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kao-...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will Kao-chan be coming?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What does Kao-chan say\Nabout all this? Kao-chan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't be jealous of music.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But of course I am...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I can think\Nof is Kao-chan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm such...a horrible girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best. I don't\Nknow what the results will be,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to give it my best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound of the scissors, ringing in my ears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His hair, a little hard to cut.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A scene of little significance passes me by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my onigiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Aren't you on a diet, Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this time turns out to be\Nprecious for Kousei as well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that would make me happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting myself in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have to wait for your daily\Ncall from your friend with the glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's not coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:09.91,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13:00 - Examination Room A\N10:00 - 17:00 Examination Room B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I think he's in the thick of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is No. 4, Kashima-san here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right? This egg salad sandwich is\Nlight on the mayo and light on the salt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which brings out its sweetness to the max!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And since they get these range-free eggs directly from the farms,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you can say it's the ultimate egg salad sandwich,\Nseeking to capture the splendid taste of the egg itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}N-Nothing's coming up but gastric juices.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh gross! Why the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Emi... Arima...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just hurled right now, you know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right? This egg salad sandwich is light\Non the mayo and light on the salt,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which brings out its sweetness to the max!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And since they get these range-free\Neggs directly from the farms,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you can say it's the ultimate egg\Nsalad sandwich, seeking to capture the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,splendid taste of the egg itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you put a thick slice of ham\Nin there, it would be even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's tough not to pick\Nthe ones with extra mayo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you crave some tea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but katsudon's a real man's meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The florentines here are delicious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we're having tea, I'd rather have scones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The best milk is Moo Moo Brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The best kind of tea is Darjeeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're really getting into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like fillet cutlet sandwiches best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See the chemistry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. 8, Takeshi Aiza-kun.\NPlease get ready in the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could fire off a cool parting shot\Nor something, but I can't think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's because...you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're musicians, so everything's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...gotta be expressed in music, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, man, what an anticlimax.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All my nervous energy - gone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I feel like something's off. Those guys...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...always getting in my way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you ready?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is your mind ready?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, let's go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Takeshi Aiza!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the stage where I'm\Nparting ways with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Ever since I was a kid, I hated being bored.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Konnyaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next I'm gonna get Class Elephant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Take-chan of Class Giraffe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My mother, who grew pessimistic about my\Nfuture and the Aiza family's reputation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}made me take all kinds of lessons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One of them was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Piano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should have him learn from\Nsomeone who's more of an expert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I win, I get a chogokin robot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Piano's a breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just watch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Emi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna destroy you all at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go. Takeshi Aiza!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chopin's Étude Op. 10, No. 12.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go! Takeshi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so lame... It's humiliating.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've disappointed my audience,\NI've made my kid sister worry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my enemies are\Nthrowing me their support.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So humiliating...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm no different than I was as a kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darn it! How could I... Whoa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:16:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could I lose to that cold-blooded\Nexpressionless girl and that sissy four-eyed jerk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! He raced all the way\Nup Hyakudan Hill without stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why didn't I see it before?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I was the one who\Nunderstood you better than anyone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when I saw you for\Nthe first time in two years...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're still in mid-journey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He must've found it. A reason to play.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it's an ugly performance, then\Nthat's the best I can do right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I kind of get it now.\NIt was always like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:17:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were the one who expanded my world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I never imagined\Nthat you'd show up like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The scenery that I'm looking for, and the sights\Nthat you wanted to see.. They're different, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Immerse yourself. Immerse yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Deeper and deeper.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, Takeshi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Contrary to appearances,\Nhe wants give a solid performance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Try to really understand the composer's aim.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Follow in your predecessors' footsteps,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and experience the feel of blood\Nand sweat-soaked score sheets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No need to become Kousei Arima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the one, Takeshi Aiza, who\Nbelongs to that line of pianists.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now this is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Takeshi's piano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How cheeky. Are you going to push\Nevery inch of your intent through?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Humph! You little punk with\Nthat shallow jerk on retainer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How dare you project such sensuality?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move forward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move forward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not just allies who support each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From your enemies, you learn\Nso much, and gain so much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until the day you meet again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just knowing they exist helps\Nyou to withstand the loneliness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those who compete, even if they're\Nenemies, help each other out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been waiting for this day for two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't feel the slightest shred of boredom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I can smash everything\NI have into something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not gonna lose next time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna demolish you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are amazing guys I can crash\Ninto, with every fiber of my being!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so lucky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome home. My hero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's back in full force!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima-sensei's competing too, so am I\Nsupposed to cheer him on, or Brother?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tragic Nagi. What a cliché!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see that a troublemaker's been awakened...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chopin just smiled...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Takeshi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still have one more number to play.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were good. Especially the Chopin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The second piece was really hard. What\Nwas up with that whole atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You created that atmosphere\Nyourself, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should've played the Chopin piece second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I reach him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I able to reach him with my music?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like you guys?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about messing\Nup here, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cause I'm so gonna destroy\Nyou in the final round!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh. After\Nthat shaky second piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better dial down the bravado...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know what they say - all bark and no bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You better not have made\Na move on my kid sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grr! Make a damn move!
